nodes_schema

NODE - Retrieve

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-fib-common-oper:mpls-forwarding/nodes/node/{node-name}/

Retrieve operation of resource: node

node-name: string
in path

ID of node-name

200 OK
node_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

Response Content-Types: application/json
